00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:16,700
Soup du jour,
Hot hors d'oeuvres

847
00:36:16,500 --> 00:36:18,400
Why, we only live to serve

848
00:36:18,300 --> 00:36:19,700
Try the gray stuff

849
