After all, Miss, this is France

853
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:31,300
And a dinner here
is never second best

854
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,500
Go on, unfold your menu

855
00:36:33,300 --> 00:36:35,400
Take a glance and then

856
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:36,400
You'll be our guest

